All the accessories are listed in a separate book, but I have that,
too, and you can probably get it by calling Dremel and asking for
Customer Service at 414 554-1390. The book does list a seven-piece
drill set, which ranges from 1/32 to 1/8 inch. My book is from 1995,
and the price then was $11.65. I've also bought polishing stuff,
cutoff wheels and various bits from Sears. And, really, you can use
any small twist drill in the tool.

Marshall

